61
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:55,420
In addition to the event in Singapore last year,

62
00:06:55,420 --> 00:07:03,920
there was also a three-seas house event in Thailand in 2024.

63
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:12,920
It also gathered dozens and nearly hundreds of ETAFORM developers,

64
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:15,420
