67
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:26,420
This is also the foundation of ETAFORM's application alliance.

68
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:30,920
The Three Seas House has been in operation for three consecutive years.

69
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:34,920
The first one in 2023 was in China,

70
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:40,920
