71
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,920
There was also a month's time.

72
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,920
In the second half of 2023,

73
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:49,420
almost 300 people arrived at the site.

74
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:51,920
Some people stayed for one or two weeks and left.

75
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:55,420
Some people stayed longer.

76
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:59,420
Basically, based on these two foundations,

77
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:02,920
one is that we think that ETAFORM technology has arrived

78
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:06,920
and can support large-scale commercial applications.

79
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:10,920
The other is that in the past two, three, four, five years,

80
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:15,920
we have done some specific things in the form of the Three Seas House.

81
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:18,920
In the third quarter, the influence of the Three Seas House

82
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,420
has even exceeded that of Asia.

83
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:24,420
It has already had a very, very big impact in Africa.

84
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:28,420
So next, ETAFORM,

85
00:08:28,420 --> 00:08:37,420
we are planning to do an ETAFORM event in Africa,

86
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:44,180
to really mobilize the African developers.

87
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:49,680
This is the origin of ETAFORM

88
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:54,680
and the preparation work that we have done before.

89
00:08:54,680 --> 00:09:00,440
This afternoon at 4.30 p.m.,

90
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:05,440
we had a one-and-a-half-hour chat with Vittaric.

91
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:12,440
What we want to discuss is the application of ETAFORM.

92
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:15,440
From his point of view and from my point of view,

93
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:18,940
we want to discuss the future applications of ETAFORM.

94
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:23,940
What may be the trend, what may be the scenario,

95
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:26,940
