96
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:33,440
Yesterday, we also announced that

97
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:36,440
the three major technologies,

98
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:41,440
the blockchain, the zero-sensitivity certification,

99
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:44,440
